==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: firecracker
<hw>fire"crack`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A small
explosive device consisting of a paper or cardboard cylinder having only
sufficient explosive mixture to make a loud bang, ignited by a short
fuse, and used mostly as an entertainment or in celebrations. Same as
<er>Cracker</er>., <pos>n.</pos>, 3.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Firecrest</ent>⟦br⟧
